  schema:name "Reading Financial Statements" ;
  schema:description "After completing this lesson, you'll be able to read the three primary [financial statements](../terms/financial-statements.md) — the balance sheet, the income statement, and the cash flow statement — identify what each one tells you about a business, and explain how the three statements connect to form a single interlocking picture." ;
